  <paragraph id="hd_id3155064" role="heading" level="1" oldref="1" l10n="U" xml-lang="en-US"><link href="text/smath/main0103.xhp" name="View">View</link></paragraph>
  <paragraph xml-lang="en-US" oldref="2" role="paragraph" id="par_id3147338" l10n="U">Sets the display scale and defines which elements you want to be visible. Most of the commands that you can enter into the <emph>Commands</emph> window can also be accessed through a mouse click if you have already opened the Selection window with <link href="text/smath/01/03090000.xhp" name="View - Selection">View - Selection</link>.</paragraph>
